**THE PROBLEM:** Waiting weeks to launch "perfect" site.

**THE FIX:**
- Launch in 24 hours validated
- Iterate based on data
- Good enough &gt; perfect
- Speed is competitive advantage
- Customer feedback &gt; your opinion

